<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title><%= title %></title>

    <!-- Favicon -->
    <link rel="icon" type="image/png" href="/favicon.png">
    <link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg">
    <link rel="shortcut icon" href="/favicon.png">

    <!-- Bootstrap 5 CSS -->
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.2/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <!-- Bootstrap Icons -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap-icons@1.11.1/font/bootstrap-icons.css">
    <!-- SortableJS para drag and drop -->
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/sortablejs@1.15.0/Sortable.min.js"></script>

    <style>
        body {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            min-height: 100vh;
            padding: 20px 0;
        }

        .main-card {
            border: none;
            border-radius: 15px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.98);
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
        }

        .year-selector {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            border: none;
            border-radius: 10px;
            color: white;
            font-weight: bold;
            padding: 12px 20px;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
        }

        .year-selector:focus {
            box-shadow: 0 0 0 0.25rem rgba(102, 126, 234, 0.25);
            border-color: #667eea;
        }

        .fluxo-table {
            font-size: 0.9rem;
        }

        .fluxo-table th {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f8f9fa 0%, #e9ecef 100%);
            border-bottom: 2px solid #667eea;
            font-weight: 600;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 12px 8px;
        }

        .fluxo-table td {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 10px 8px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #e9ecef;
            font-weight: 500;
        }

        .conta-cell {
            text-align: left !important;
            min-width: 200px;
            background: rgba(248, 249, 250, 0.5);
            font-weight: 600;
            padding: 12px 15px; /* Adicionar mais padding para acomodar o bot√£o */
        }

        .valor-positivo {
            color: #28a745;
        }

        .valor-negativo {
            color: #dc3545;
        }

        .valor-zero {
            color: #6c757d;
            opacity: 0.7;
        }

        .total-row {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            color: white;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        .total-row td {
            border-bottom: none;
            padding: 15px 8px;
        }

        .mes-header {
            writing-mode: horizontal-tb;
            min-width: 90px;
        }

        .table-container {
            border-radius: 10px;
            border: 1px solid #dee2e6;
        }

        .breadcrumb {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
            border-radius: 10px;
        }

        .header-actions {
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
        }

        .icon-tipo {
            margin-right: 8px;
        }

        .badge-categoria {
            font-size: 0.7rem;
            opacity: 0.8;
        }


        /* Responsividade */
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .fluxo-table {
                font-size: 0.8rem;
            }

            .fluxo-table th,
            .fluxo-table td {
                padding: 8px 4px;
            }

            .mes-header {
                min-width: 70px;
            }

            .conta-cell {
                min-width: 150px;
            }
        }

        /* Anima√ß√µes */
        .table-fade-in {
            animation: fadeIn 0.5s ease-in;
        }

        @keyframes fadeIn {
            from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(10px); }
            to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
        }

        /* Estilos da Modal de Nova Conta */
        .modal-header {
            border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
        }

        .modal-body .form-label {
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }

        .modal-body .form-control:focus,
        .modal-body .form-select:focus {
            border-color: #667eea;
            box-shadow: 0 0 0 0.25rem rgba(102, 126, 234, 0.25);
        }

        .modal-body .alert-info {
            background-color: rgba(102, 126, 234, 0.1);
            border-color: rgba(102, 126, 234, 0.2);
            color: #495057;
        }

        .modal .btn-primary {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            border: none;
        }

        .modal .btn-primary:hover {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #5a67d8 0%, #6b46c1 100%);
            transform: translateY(-1px);
        }

        /* Valida√ß√£o visual melhorada */
        .was-validated .form-control:valid,
        .was-validated .form-select:valid {
            border-color: #28a745;
        }

        .was-validated .form-control:invalid,
        .was-validated .form-select:invalid {
            border-color: #dc3545;
        }

        /* Estilos da Modal de Nova Movimenta√ß√£o */
        .modal-movimentacao .modal-header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #28a745 0%, #20c997 100%);
        }

        /* C√©lulas clic√°veis da tabela */
        .celula-clicavel {
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: all 0.2s ease;
            position: relative;
            border: 1px solid transparent;
        }

        .celula-clicavel:hover {
            background-color: rgba(40, 167, 69, 0.08);
            border-color: rgba(40, 167, 69, 0.3);
            transform: scale(1.01);
            box-shadow: 0 2px 4px rgba(40, 167, 69, 0.1);
        }

        .celula-clicavel:active {
            background-color: rgba(40, 167, 69, 0.15);
            transform: scale(0.99);
        }

        /* Indicator de c√©lula clic√°vel */
        .celula-clicavel::after {
            content: "+";
            position: absolute;
            top: 3px;
            right: 6px;
            font-size: 12px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #28a745;
            opacity: 0;
            transition: opacity 0.2s ease;
        }

        .celula-clicavel:hover::after {
            opacity: 0.7;
        }

        /* N√£o aplicar efeitos nas c√©lulas de total */
        .total-row .celula-clicavel {
            cursor: default;
            pointer-events: none;
        }

        .total-row .celula-clicavel::after {
            display: none;
        }

        /* Campo de valor com formata√ß√£o */
        #movValor {
            text-align: right;
            font-weight: bold;
            font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
        }

        /* Readonly fields styling */
        .form-control[readonly],
        .form-select[disabled] {
            background-color: #f8f9fa !important;
            opacity: 1;
        }

        /* Estilos para conta especial */
        .conta-especial {
            background-color: rgba(255, 193, 7, 0.05);
            border-left: 3px solid #ffc107;
        }

        .conta-especial-cell {
            background-color: rgba(255, 193, 7, 0.08);
            cursor: not-allowed;
            position: relative;
        }

        .conta-especial-cell::after {
            content: "üîí";
            position: absolute;
            top: 3px;
            right: 6px;
            font-size: 10px;
            opacity: 0.5;
        }

        .conta-especial .conta-cell {
            background-color: rgba(255, 193, 7, 0.1);
        }

        /* Estilos para drag and drop */
        .conta-row {
            cursor: move;
            transition: all 0.2s ease;
        }

        .conta-row:hover {
            box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
        }

        .conta-row.sortable-ghost {
            opacity: 0.4;
            background: rgba(108, 117, 125, 0.2);
        }

        .conta-row.sortable-drag {
            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
            transform: rotate(2deg);
        }

        /* Saldo anterior n√£o pode ser arrastado */
        .conta-especial {
            cursor: not-allowed !important;
        }

        .drag-handle {
            cursor: move;
            color: #6c757d;
            opacity: 0.6;
            margin-right: 8px;
            transition: opacity 0.2s ease;
        }

        .conta-row:hover .drag-handle {
            opacity: 1;
        }

        .conta-especial .drag-handle {
            cursor: not-allowed;
            opacity: 0.3;
        }

        /* Feedback visual durante drag */
        .sortable-chosen {
            background: rgba(40, 167, 69, 0.1) !important;
        }

        /* Melhor indica√ß√£o para contas sem movimenta√ß√£o */
        .celula-clicavel .valor-zero {
            opacity: 0.6;
            font-style: italic;
        }

        .celula-clicavel:hover .valor-zero {
            opacity: 1;
            font-style: normal;
        }

        /* Dica visual para contas vazias */
        .celula-clicavel.conta-vazia {
            background-color: rgba(108, 117, 125, 0.03);
        }

        .celula-clicavel.conta-vazia:hover {
            background-color: rgba(40, 167, 69, 0.08);
        }

        /* Estilos para Nova Categoria */
        #novaCategoriaDiv {
            border-left: 3px solid #28a745;
            padding-left: 15px;
            background-color: rgba(40, 167, 69, 0.05);
            border-radius: 5px;
        }

        #categoriaId option[value="nova"] {
            background-color: #e8f5e8;
            color: #155724;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        #novaCategoriaNome:focus {
            border-color: #28a745;
            box-shadow: 0 0 0 0.25rem rgba(40, 167, 69, 0.25);
        }

        .nova-categoria-feedback {
            color: #28a745;
            font-size: 0.875em;
        }

        /* Bot√£o Nova Conta no cabe√ßalho da tabela */
        .conta-cell .btn-outline-primary {
            border-color: rgba(102, 126, 234, 0.6);
            color: #667eea;
            border-width: 1px;
            padding: 2px 6px;
            font-size: 0.7rem;
            line-height: 1.2;
            transition: all 0.2s ease;
            border-radius: 4px;
            opacity: 0.8;
        }

        .conta-cell .btn-outline-primary:hover {
            background-color: #667eea;
            border-color: #667eea;
            color: white;
            transform: scale(1.1);
            opacity: 1;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 4px rgba(102, 126, 234, 0.3);
        }

        .conta-cell .btn-outline-primary:focus {
            box-shadow: 0 0 0 0.2rem rgba(102, 126, 234, 0.25);
            opacity: 1;
        }

        /* Manter o layout do cabe√ßalho bem organizado */
        .conta-cell .d-flex {
            min-height: 20px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container-fluid">
        <!-- Breadcrumb -->
        <nav aria-label="breadcrumb" class="mb-4">
            <ol class="breadcrumb">
                <li class="breadcrumb-item"><a href="/"><i class="bi bi-house"></i> In√≠cio</a></li>
                <li class="breadcrumb-item"><a href="/fluxo-caixa"><i class="bi bi-graph-up"></i> Dashboard</a></li>
                <li class="breadcrumb-item active" aria-current="page">
                    <i class="bi bi-table"></i> Fluxo de Caixa
                </li>
            </ol>
        </nav>

        <!-- Header com Controles -->
        <div class="header-actions">
            <div class="row align-items-center">
                <div class="col">
                    <h1 class="text-white mb-0">
                        <i class="bi bi-table me-2"></i>Fluxo de Caixa Anual
                    </h1>
                    <p class="text-white-50 mb-0">Vis√£o consolidada por conta e m√™s</p>
                </div>
                <div class="col-auto">
                    <div class="d-flex align-items-center gap-3">
                        <!-- Seletor de Ano -->
                        <div class="d-flex align-items-center">
                            <label class="text-white me-2 fw-bold">Ano:</label>
                            <select id="yearSelector" class="form-select year-selector">
                                <% anosDisponiveis.forEach(function(ano) { %>
                                <option value="<%= ano %>" <%= ano === anoSelecionado ? 'selected' : '' %>>
                                    <%= ano %>
                                </option>
                                <% }); %>
                            </select>
                        </div>

                        <!-- A√ß√µes -->
                        <div class="btn-group" role="group">
                            <a href="/fluxo-caixa/movimentacoes/add" class="btn btn-outline-light">
                                <i class="bi bi-plus-circle me-2"></i>Nova Movimenta√ß√£o
                            </a>
                            <a href="/fluxo-caixa/movimentacoes" class="btn btn-outline-light">
                                <i class="bi bi-list me-2"></i>Ver Movimenta√ß√µes
                            </a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Mensagens -->
        <% if (message) { %>
        <div class="alert alert-success alert-dismissible fade show" role="alert">
            <i class="bi bi-check-circle me-2"></i><%= message %>
            <button type="button" class="btn-close" data-bs-dismiss="alert"></button>
        </div>
        <% } %>
        <% if (error) { %>
        <div class="alert alert-danger alert-dismissible fade show" role="alert">
            <i class="bi bi-exclamation-triangle me-2"></i><%= error %>
            <button type="button" class="btn-close" data-bs-dismiss="alert"></button>
        </div>
        <% } %>

        <!-- Tabela Principal -->
        <div class="card main-card">
            <div class="card-header bg-transparent border-0 pb-2">
                <div class="d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center">
                    <h5 class="card-title mb-0">
                        <i class="bi bi-calendar3 me-2"></i>Fluxo de Caixa - <%= anoSelecionado %>
                    </h5>
                    <div class="text-end">
                        <small class="text-muted">Total Geral:</small>
                        <div class="fw-bold fs-5 <%= totalGeral >= 0 ? 'valor-positivo' : 'valor-negativo' %>">
                            R$ <%= Math.abs(totalGeral).toFixed(2).replace('.', ',') %>
                            <% if (totalGeral < 0) { %><small class="text-muted">(negativo)</small><% } %>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="card-body p-0">
                <div class="table-container table-fade-in">
                    <table class="table table-hover fluxo-table mb-0">
                        <thead>
                            <tr>
                                <th class="conta-cell">
                                    <div class="d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center">
                                        <span>
                                            <i class="bi bi-building me-2"></i>Conta
                                        </span>
                                        <button type="button" class="btn btn-sm btn-outline-primary"
                                                data-bs-toggle="modal" data-bs-target="#novaContaModal"
                                                title="Adicionar nova conta">
                                            <i class="bi bi-plus"></i>
                                        </button>
                                    </div>
                                </th>
                                <% nomesMeses.forEach(function(mes, index) { %>
                                <th class="mes-header">
                                    <%= mes.substring(0, 3) %>
                                    <br><small class="text-muted">
                                        <%= (index + 1).toString().padStart(2, '0') %>
                                    </small>
                                </th>
                                <% }); %>
                                <th class="mes-header">
                                    <strong>M√©dia</strong>
                                    <br><small class="text-muted">do Ano</small>
                                </th>
                            </tr>
                        </thead>
                        <tbody id="contas-tbody">
                            <% Object.values(dadosPorContaMes).forEach(function(item) { %>
                            <tr class="conta-row <%= item.conta.id === 999 ? 'conta-especial' : '' %>"
                                data-conta-id="<%= item.conta.id %>">
                                <td class="conta-cell">
                                    <div class="d-flex align-items-center">
                                        <i class="bi bi-grip-vertical drag-handle"
                                           title="<%= item.conta.id === 999 ? 'Posi√ß√£o fixa - n√£o pode ser movida' : 'Arrastar para reordenar' %>"></i>
                                        <i class="<%= getIconeTipoConta(item.conta.tipoConta) %> text-<%= getCorTipoConta(item.conta.tipoConta) %> icon-tipo"></i>
                                        <div>
                                            <div class="fw-semibold">
                                                <%= item.conta.nomeConta %>
                                                <% if (item.conta.id === 999) { %>
                                                <small class="badge bg-warning text-dark ms-2">
                                                    <i class="bi bi-lock-fill"></i> Autom√°tica
                                                </small>
                                                <% } %>
                                            </div>
                                            <small class="badge badge-categoria bg-light text-dark">
                                                <%= item.conta.categoriaConta.categoria %>
                                            </small>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </td>
                                <% for (let mes = 0; mes < 12; mes++) { %>
                                <% const valor = item.meses[mes]; %>
                                <td class="<%= item.conta.id === 999 ? 'conta-especial-cell' : 'celula-clicavel' %><%= valor === 0 && item.conta.id !== 999 ? ' conta-vazia' : '' %>"
                                    <% if (item.conta.id !== 999) { %>
                                    data-conta-id="<%= item.conta.id %>"
                                    data-conta-nome="<%= item.conta.nomeConta %>"
                                    data-conta-tipo="<%= item.conta.tipoConta %>"
                                    data-conta-categoria="<%= item.conta.categoriaConta.categoria %>"
                                    data-mes="<%= mes %>"
                                    data-ano="<%= anoSelecionado %>"
                                    <% if (valor === 0) { %>
                                    title="Clique para adicionar primeira movimenta√ß√£o em <%= nomesMeses[mes] %>/<%= anoSelecionado %> - Conta sem movimenta√ß√µes"
                                    <% } else { %>
                                    title="Clique para adicionar movimenta√ß√£o em <%= nomesMeses[mes] %>/<%= anoSelecionado %>"
                                    <% } %>
                                    <% } else { %>
                                    title="Saldo calculado automaticamente do m√™s anterior"
                                    <% } %>>
                                    <span class="<%= valor > 0 ? 'valor-positivo' : valor < 0 ? 'valor-negativo' : 'valor-zero' %>">
                                        <% if (valor !== 0) { %>
                                            R$ <%= Math.abs(valor).toFixed(2).replace('.', ',') %>
                                            <% if (valor < 0) { %><br><small class="text-muted">(d√©bito)</small><% } %>
                                        <% } else { %>
                                            -
                                        <% } %>
                                    </span>
                                </td>
                                <% } %>
                                <td>
                                    <% const mediaConta = totaisPorConta[item.conta.ordemTabela]; %>
                                    <% if (item.conta.tipoConta === 'SALDO') { %>
                                        <span class="text-muted" style="font-style: italic;">
                                            N/A
                                        </span>
                                    <% } else { %>
                                        <strong class="<%= mediaConta > 0 ? 'valor-positivo' : mediaConta < 0 ? 'valor-negativo' : 'valor-zero' %>">
                                            <% if (mediaConta !== 0) { %>
                                                R$ <%= Math.abs(mediaConta).toFixed(2).replace('.', ',') %>
                                                <% if (mediaConta < 0) { %><br><small class="text-muted">(d√©bito)</small><% } %>
                                                <br><small class="text-muted">m√©dia</small>
                                            <% } else { %>
                                                -
                                            <% } %>
                                        </strong>
                                    <% } %>
                                </td>
                            </tr>
                            <% }); %>
                        </tbody>
                        <tfoot>
                            <tr class="total-row">
                                <td class="conta-cell">
                                    <strong><i class="bi bi-calculator me-2"></i>TOTAL MENSAL</strong>
                                </td>
                                <% for (let mes = 0; mes < 12; mes++) { %>
                                <td class="total-cell">
                                    <% const totalMes = totaisPorMes[mes]; %>
                                    <strong>
                                        <% if (totalMes !== 0) { %>
                                            R$ <%= Math.abs(totalMes).toFixed(2).replace('.', ',') %>
                                            <% if (totalMes < 0) { %><br><small>(d√©bito)</small><% } %>
                                        <% } else { %>
                                            -
                                        <% } %>
                                    </strong>
                                </td>
                                <% } %>
                                <td>
                                    <!-- Campo em branco - sem total anual -->
                                </td>
                            </tr>
                        </tfoot>
                    </table>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Footer com Informa√ß√µes -->
        <div class="row mt-4">
            <div class="col-md-8">
                <div class="card main-card">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h6 class="card-title">
                            <i class="bi bi-info-circle me-2"></i>Legenda
                        </h6>
                        <div class="row">
                            <div class="col-md-4">
                                <div class="d-flex align-items-center mb-2">
                                    <i class="bi bi-arrow-up-circle text-success me-2"></i>
                                    <span class="valor-positivo">Valores Positivos</span>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="col-md-4">
                                <div class="d-flex align-items-center mb-2">
                                    <i class="bi bi-arrow-down-circle text-danger me-2"></i>
                                    <span class="valor-negativo">Valores Negativos</span>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="col-md-4">
                                <div class="d-flex align-items-center mb-2">
                                    <i class="bi bi-dash-circle text-muted me-2"></i>
                                    <span class="valor-zero">Sem Movimenta√ß√£o</span>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="row">
                            <div class="col-md-6">
                                <div class="d-flex align-items-center mb-2">
                                    <i class="bi bi-calculator text-primary me-2"></i>
                                    <span class="text-primary">M√©dia Mensal</span>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="col-md-6">
                                <div class="d-flex align-items-center mb-2">
                                    <i class="bi bi-x-circle text-muted me-2"></i>
                                    <span class="text-muted">N/A (Contas de Saldo)</span>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <hr>
                        <div class="d-flex align-items-center mb-2">
                            <i class="bi bi-lock-fill text-warning me-2"></i>
                            <span class="text-warning"><strong>Saldo Anterior (Autom√°tica)</strong></span>
                        </div>
                        <small class="text-muted">
                            <i class="bi bi-calendar-check me-1"></i>
                            Dados consolidados para o ano de <strong><%= anoSelecionado %></strong>.
                            Total de <%= Object.keys(dadosPorContaMes).length %> contas exibidas (todas as contas cadastradas).
                            <br>
                            <i class="bi bi-info-circle me-1"></i>
                            A conta "Saldo Anterior" √© calculada automaticamente com base no saldo do m√™s anterior.
                            <br>
                            <i class="bi bi-calculator me-1"></i>
                            A coluna "M√©dia Mensal" mostra a m√©dia dos meses com movimenta√ß√£o no ano selecionado (contas de saldo n√£o possuem m√©dia).
                            <br>
                            <i class="bi bi-table me-1"></i>
                            Contas sem movimenta√ß√µes no ano aparecem com valores zerados, mas podem receber novos valores a qualquer momento.
                        </small>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <div class="card main-card">
